English:
Restaurants must;
1.ensure quality & safety of food, rinse &sanitize food contact surfaces, disinfect surfaces, floors & counters.
2.Install adequate portable running water & accessible washing basins for hand washing purposes, at the entrance & exit points.

Kiswahili:
Mikahawa lazima;
1. kuhakikisha ubora na usalama wa chakula, suuza na usafi wa nyuso zinazogusa chakula, safisha nyuso, sakafu na kaunta.
2. Weka maji ya kutosha yanayobebeka na beseni za kufulia zinazoweza kufikika kwa ajili ya kunawia mikono, kwenye sehemu za kuingilia na za kutokea.
